Amiga E Encyclopedia - Persons

This file contains the persons involved in this project, the ones that joined,
are or will be contacted. There are remarks about each which include e-mail
address und possible subject they would write on.


The involved persons are:

  Gregor Goldbach (glauschwuffel@amt.comlink.de, general knowledge about
                   every major lib up to os2.04 except math; printer.device,
                   E3.1a reg:

    intuition: screens, windows, gadgets
    graphics:  borders, images, areas
    exec:      messages, lists
    dos:       in/output,
    gadtools:  minor
    [maybe porting of newiff if needed]

    E:         not very well: lisp-cells,
               not at all:    unification


