    Dan Thies (rtfm@cyberspace.com)

'I can provide improved documentation on converting .fd and .i files to .m
files, for the addition of shared libraries to E. I could also provide quite
extensive information on OO programming in E. Other than that, I probably
would have time to deal with the Intuition section, since I have already
rewritten most of the 2.04 RKM material on that in E.  If we want to split up
intuition, I could provide information on screens, windows, and (probably)
IDCMP pretty quickly.'

